Comment: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:49.69,OP1-Eng,,0,0,0,karaoke,I feel like I can go anywhere
Comment: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:54.00,OP1-Eng,,0,0,0,karaoke,Listen to your heart
Comment: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.40,OP1-Eng,,0,0,0,karaoke,Entrust yourself to its beat
Comment: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:02.60,OP1-Eng,,0,0,0,karaoke,Stand strong against the blowing wind
